            <li>Republish material from {siteConfig.title}</li>
            <li>Sell, rent or sub-license material from {siteConfig.title}</li>
            <li>
                Reproduce, duplicate or copy material from {siteConfig.title}
            </li>
            <li>Redistribute content from {siteConfig.title}</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
            Hyperlinking to our Content
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            The following organizations may link to our Website without prior
            written approval:
